id="post-4319" class="post-4319 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-food-body-mind tag-farm tag-food-tank tag-think-tank"><h2 class="entry-title"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2014/03/10/food-tank-is-a-think-tank-for-food/" title="Permalink to Food Tank is a Think Tank for Food" rel="bookmark">Food Tank is a Think Tank for Food</a></h2><div
class="entry-meta"> <span
class="entry-date" title="2014/03/10 11:41 am"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2014/03/10/food-tank-is-a-think-tank-for-food/" title="Food Tank is a Think Tank for Food" rel="bookmark">2014/03/10 11:41 am</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="comments-link"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2014/03/10/food-tank-is-a-think-tank-for-food/#comments">Leave a Comment</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="entry-author author vcard"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/author/administrator/" title="by Adam Clare" rel="author">Adam Clare</a></span></div><div
class="entry-content clearfix"><p><iframe
width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/TQd6LpBVxIk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a
href="http://foodtank.com">Food Tank </a>is a new initiative to bring attention to the complexity of food systems. They aim to educate people about how foods gets from the ground to your table &#8211; and how that process relates to the world at large. Here&#8217;s a recent release of their&#8217;s looking at the positive impact of family farmers:</p><blockquote><p>Family farmers—small and large enhance biodiversity, protect natural resources, and improve local economies. The video highlights how family farmers, small and large, are using innovative agroecological practices to increase yields, improve incomes, and foster environmental sustainability. And Food Tank emphasizes how family farmers are a critical line of defense against economic disparity, water scarcity, deforestation, and extreme weather events.</p></blockquote><p><a
href="http://foodtank.com/news/2014/02/video-release-family-farmers-you-a-well-nourished-world">Read more.</a></p><div
